column5: ok guys here is another try at this.....temagami weather was awsome...ice road was a bit rough..i only have some of the pictures for now and will have more as soon as my buddies send me more of the pictures...fishing was tough but we found them..we also did some spec fishing as you can see..this is one days catch...a great time was had by all and i cant wait to get back there may 31st for some spring fishing...you never know...i might just slip away for one more weekend if anyone is going up and has some room for me...we filmed a fox who looked to be hungry take a look at the video....i would like to thank glen (GCD ) for helping me post this report....     us driving in with gear     me and the boys        some fish  a little fox action
